gpio/twl4030: get platform data from device tree

Adds a number of missing device tree properties for
twl4030/gpio, and update bindings:
- "ti,use-leds"  -> .use_leds
- "ti,debounce"  -> .debounce
- "ti,mmc-cd"    -> .mmc_cd
- "ti,pullups"   -> .pullups
- "ti,pulldowns" -> .pulldowns

